  "body": "### Description\nUpdate validator client to track and perform duties for producing sync signatures.  As per https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/v1.1.0-alpha.2/specs/altair/validator.md#sync-committee-signatures\n\n* Request sync committee duties from beacon node\n* Request beacon node subscribe to sync committee subnets\n    * Beacon node should update it's ENR to report which subnets it is subscribed to\n* Produce sync committee signature for every slot in the sync committee period and publish via beacon node to subnet",
